le=\"color: rgb(51, 144, 240);font-size: 21px;border: none;\">best kidney specialist in Delhi</a>, India</strong> and transplant physician.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Best Kidney Specialists in India</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">If you&rsquo;re endeavoring to get a high-class treatment at a minimal price as compared to international hospitals, Kidney Total Care India is your stoppage. Browse it and get to know more about our nephrologist services in India and treatments we do of kidney and urinary system. It is the place where <a href=\"https://www.kidneytotalcareindia.com/\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 144, 240);font-size: 21px;border: none;\"><strong>Best nephrologist in India</strong></a> Dr. Sunil Prakash gives his services. A professional <strong><a href=\"https://www.kidneytotalcareindia.com/\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 144, 240);font-size: 21px;border: none;\">kidney specialist in Delhi</a>, India</strong> Dr. Sunil Prakash proficient in diagnoses and treatment of kidney giving world-class health services in India. The treatments we do are kidney inflammation, chronic disease in kidney, kidney transplant surgery, renal disorders, kidney stones and many more.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Proper health care is the key to living a healthy life, we promise to make you healthier, undertaking all yours suffering by giving best class kidney treatments in India.</span></p>', '2024-09-26', '[\"best nephrologist in India\", \"kidney specialist in India\", \"nephrologist treatments in India\"]', 'best-nephrologist-in-india'),
(10, 'Choosing Best Nephrologist in India To Keep Well Kidney Functions', 'Kidney diseases profoundly affect sexual wellbeing, health, the capacity to consider, and so forth. You will find the...', 'ChoosingBest.png', '<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Kidney diseases profoundly affect sexual wellbeing, health, the capacity to consider, and so forth. You will find the issues identified with unending kidney illness and pregnancy in my next post. For now, how about we attempt and see how and why a diminishment in your kidney capacity could influence your sexual wellbeing. Sexual brokenness tends to decline as kidney infection advances and is a piece of the star grouping of different signs and side effects of critical kidney illness. On the off chance that you discover anything not acceptable, you can search for <a href=\"https://www.kidneytotalcareindia.com/\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 144, 240);font-size: 21px;border: none;\"><strong>best kidney specialist in Delhi</strong></a>, India.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Diseases are increasing in human a body at vast speed. The result of this development increases so much pollution which causes many health problems. Kidney disease is the most common disease spreading in India at a very large rate. People suffering from kidney problems are growing in very large volume in all over India. A kidney is an important organ of the human body. Its main function is to filter the waste material by regulating different functions in the body.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">A kidney is a pair of organs present in the abnormal cavities of the human body helpful to excrete urine. Kidneys are in bean-like shape plays an essential role in vertebrates. The paired rental arteries pass blood to kidneys and kidneys drain the blood into the paired renal vein. Kidney discharges urine into a ureter which empties it into the bladder. If you are suffering from Kidney failure then the requirement of adequate and timely treatment is a necessity.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Main Functionalities of Kidney</span></strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\' color: rgb(42, 42, 42); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; font-family: \"border: none;\"; list-style-type: disc;\'>\r\n    <li style=\"font-size: 22px; border: none;\">Removal of waste products of metabolism.</li>\r\n    <li style=\"font-size: 22px; border: none;\">To regulate the balance of electrolytes in the blood.</li>\r\n    <li style=\"font-size: 22px; border: none;\">Maintains pH homeostasis.</li>\r\n    <li style=\"font-size: 22px; border: none;\">Removal of excess molecules from the blood.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Unpredictable menses could be available in ladies with cutting edge kidney malady. More often than not, the menstrual stream has a tendency to be meager and whimsical; in any case, overwhelming draining could be seen since kidney illness interferes with platelet capacity. One reason for this unsettling influence is that the uremic poisons which collect in critical kidney sickness meddle with typical ovulation and the hormonal changes that go with that. Ovulation is a key to a typical monthly cycle, furthermore to a lady&rsquo;s capacity to get pregnant.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Ladies in critical phases of kidney illness could encounter a subjective decline in drive because of the hormonal changes specified above, also because of weakness that could be available auxiliary to the unending kidney infections and kinds of other. This further gets exacerbated by vaginal dryness that could be available also, because of low estrogen levels. A powerlessness to accomplish climax is frequently seen.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">People face the main difficulty in finding the best <strong><a href=\"https://www.kidneytotalcareindia.com/\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 144, 240);font-size: 21px;border: none;\">Kidney Specialist in Delhi</a></strong><em><strong>, India</strong></em>. The need for a nephrologist is arising because of kidney damage or not function properly. The main causes are they no longer remove wastes and extra water from the blood as they function. &nbsp;Kidney disease is most common in people who are suffering from diabetes or high blood pressure. Some of the <a href=\"https://www.kidneytotalcareindia.com/\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 144, 240);font-size: 21px;border: none;\"><strong>best kidney hospitals in India</strong></a> are available for kidney treatment.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Facts responsible for Kidney failure is the inability to remove potassium from the bloodstream which leads to abnormal heart pulse and sudden death. There are numerous factors which effect kidney failure. The first step is to underlying the disease by the best possible treatment. In India, there is so many Kidney Specialist known as a nephrologist in science language. They undertake different types of kidney disease by providing proper care. They check the situation of patients and treats accordingly.</span></p>', '2024-09-26', '[\"best kidney specialist in India\", \"best nephrologist in India\", \"kidney infection treatment\", \"nephrologist in India\"]', 'choosing-best-nephrologist-in-india-to-keep-well-kidney-functions'),
(11, 'A Specialist Treatment to Fight Kidney Failure Diseases', 'Nephrology services in a simple term we define it as a branch of medical science which deals with the study of physiology...', 'doctor-patient.jpg', '<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Nephrology services in a simple term we define it as a branch of medical science which deals with the study of physiology and kidney diseases. The word nephrology came out from the Greek word &ldquo;nephros&rdquo; which means kidney and the word &ldquo;logy&rdquo; means the study of while merging both the words nephrology formation has done. It has the specialty in kidney treatment disease like Dialysis, kidney transplantation and many more. <a href=\"https://www.kidneytotalcareindia.com/\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 144, 240);font-size: 21px;border: none;\"><strong>Nephrologist in Delhi</strong></a> deals with the problem which we face in our daily life due to systematic conditions like diabetes, autoimmune disease, which has occurred due to a kidney problem.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">The nephrology services effectiveness in the field of:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Kidney Stone Management:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"> They provide <strong><a href=\"https://www.kidneytotalcareindia.com/\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 144, 240);font-size: 21px;border: none;\">nephrology services in India</a></strong> offering diagnostic treatment with medical and surgical operations. They have experts done many kidney stone operations from years holding a great experience with high successes operations. They provide all the latest technology for kidney treatments like laser, Shockwave, invasive and noninvasive surgeries.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Renal Biopsies</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">: It is also known as kidney biopsy an operation includes removal of a small part of the kidney under a microscope to examine body parts. The test is done to examine the kidney disease by analysis of kidney tissues to provide the best kidney treatment.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><a href=\"https://www.kidneytotalcareindia.com/dialysis.html\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 144, 240);font-size: 21px;border: none;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Kidney Dialysis</span></strong></a><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">: Some people face the problem of kidney fail or damage because it cannot function properly. They do dialysis which includes removal of the harmful wastes and unwanted water from the blood.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Treatment of Acute Renal Failure</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">: it is done to prevent the kidney when it suddenly stops working or loses its filtering ability. It results in the accumulation of waste material and electrolytes in body parts which are dangerous and life taking.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Kidney &amp; Kidney-Pancreas Transplantation</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">: It is an operation that cures both kidney and pancreas failure.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Treatment of Osteoporosis and Bone Diseases</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">: It is a disease in which bones become weak more likely to break at any age due to deterioration of bone tissue.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\'color: rgb(42, 42, 42);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 21px;font-family: \"\'><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Dr. Sunil Prakash is a famous and <strong><a href=\"https://www.kidneytotalcareindia.com/\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 144, 240);font-size: 21px;border: none;\">best nephrologist in Delhi</a></strong> having experience of many years and he has worked on leading hospitals in India. He has done extraordinary services in the field of nephrology and helping to get rid of the immune and diseases.</span></p>', '2024-09-26', '[\"best kidney specialist in India\", \"best nephrologist in Delhi\", \"Kidney Failure Diseases\"]', 'a-specialist-treatment-to-fight-kidney-failure-diseases'),
